Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.53,0:00:03.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From yesterday's me to today's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:07.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You will lose your memories in thirteen hours. {You can only remember for thirteen hours}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's the impact of the accident four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's regrettable that your left eye was lost at the same time as well. {...that you lost your right eye at the same time too.  <---TL check that O_o} {That your right eye was lost at the same time?}{our? how do you refer to yourself tomorrow about your eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept that it happened and that it's the truth. {I think, when speaking formally, or in a manner of relating to it, we shouldn't use contractions. ._.;}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:25.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have written everything that you will need in order to live right here. {I have written everything that you will need in order to live here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:31.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,First, please read the diary every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,These are your memories. {These are your memories.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about you is inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:41.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Second, please make sure you write something in the diary. {leave something in the diary}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:48.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please write about that day's behavior, conversations, and other records as accurately as possible. {Please write about your behavior, conversations, and other records, as accurately as possible for that day.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:39.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Third, try to avoid any contact with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because with this kind of injury, it might cause trouble. {"... awful troubles" ..? Sounds a bit weird. Maybe... "Because with this kind of injury, problems may arise?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And there is the possibility of troubling the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:53.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever meet another person, please write about that person's character and information in the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:03:05.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I only wrote of Renji-kun as a short, school uniformed, older student who came by the station around three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Older?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:13.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because my time stopped four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:23.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The next day I didn't recognize you in normal clothes and coming by earlier than three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as you can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry. It is a diary after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is me, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:45.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen hours... so that's how long Chihiro can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:51.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I wake up at seven in the morning, I remember everything that day until eight in the evening. {7am to 8pm}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:57.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But after that, I will lose my memories slowly as each hour passes. {but she forgets her every one hour memories as time passes} {It's like buffer being filled by new data, first in first out}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:03.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,By midnight, I will only remember from eleven in the morning of the previous day. {assumning twelve at night is different day as eleven in the morning}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:12.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And the next morning after that at seven, I will only remember things from six in the evening of the previous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:18.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So tomorrow morning you will forget everything about meeting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:22.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will remember very important things by repeating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:34.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I repeat something many times, I can remember it for more than thirteen hours. {Repeat it many times and when I recall it I can remember it for more than thirteen hours.  TL check please.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:42.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Every night at nine, I remember important things by repeatedly reading my diary. {many time}{over and over}{continuously}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:46.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I can still remember them the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:54.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Renji-kun met me and the fact that I have anterograde amnesia. {memory}{Is there a medical term for this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am living an idle life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:04.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't go to school, and I don't have anyone that I can call a friend. {anyone}{If so, you wouldn't need that "that".}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really have nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:12.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I just sit idly at the station, I don't have to remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a life without meaning{value}, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier if you just throw everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.20,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,598)}That's not tr-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:31.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything, so my goal in life is to try not to cause trouble for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But even that's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just by living, I will cause trouble for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:43.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And even then, I will forget the memory of troubling someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:48.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-san, what I'm about to say is in jest. {Somehow, 'Jest' doesn't fit in the context. A better synonym would be preferred.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In jest?{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:05.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, you have the future career form, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from other moms at the cooking class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty early. You're still a first-year student.{Even though you're still a first year student.(Freshman?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to put on it? {fill in}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can just write whatever you want to be, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be worrying about it if I had already decided.{already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:31.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I need you to send something to Kuze-san after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san? He's back?{He's back?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:39.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Take the pot on top of the stove and let him know that's his, okay? {something}{check}{The second part I don't get either}{thefuck?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:48.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're still small like always.{You're still small like always.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three months and that's the first thing you say to me?{.. and that's}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that the usual food for me?{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My mother said please take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the side dish is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:18.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if you don't mind a naked woman on the bed. {clothless}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:24.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I mind so that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Worrying about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's not really something important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so...{Well, if you say so.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:37.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I'll bring some souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring the pot back when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day. {trip? Check}{Have a nice day?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:58.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just the usual peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think of that because I remember my everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was happy that I was able to see Kuze-san yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's because I remember Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:19.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for Chihiro, she only remembers thirteen hours of the day she spent and the people that she met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:26.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept meeting with Chihiro simply because I wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:35.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for Chihiro to meet a stranger like me, she always has to prepare her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She must have felt scared and worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:39.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite that... {despite that}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:50.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to meet with Chihiro with this casual feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be beside Chihiro, then prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:58.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just that I'm infatuating myself with Chihiro.{fawning? What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's not there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm about to say is in jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In jest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:23.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, I thought of how it would be for me to just disappear without troubling anyone. {Everyday I thought of how it will be for me to just disappear without troubling anyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought of how.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:31.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of myself disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I do feel afraid, then those are just my emotions.{emotions?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:34.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,However... {but}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,However...? {but}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:46.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm really afraid of isn't losing my own memories, but the thought that I'll disappear from everyone else's memories. {thought, contemplation}{Go with thought.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:52.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's pretty cowardly of me, isn't it? {cowardly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In jest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:00.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything that I can do for Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something that a knight can do in order to protect the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:07.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something... that will make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to write a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,About anything; just one story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make one with the current me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Himura-san here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:43.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The message is that Chihiro has a fever and can't come today.  She says she's sorry.{The message is "Chihiro is down with fever today so she can't come today".}{TL check with the 'gomennasai' included}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just a normal fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just for precautions, she shouldn't come outside for today.{tl check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You promised her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro waited here until late at night.{until late at night? until the middle of the night?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:14.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro will definitely keep a promise like that because she has such a memory.{Chihiro definitely will keep a promise like that because she has such a memory.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:23.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For her, a promise like, "Let's meet again tomorrow" is an important promise that connects the next day's her to the previous day's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:32.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get her, but she said that she had a promise. Such stubbornness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:39.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has just been following anything around her because she can't validate her own existence. {Chihiro has been just following anything around her because she can't validate her own existance.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:43.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess she still has human-like emotions inside of her. {other words} {but I guess she stilll has human-like emotions inside her.  Check}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... without knowing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're not responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:58.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For Chihiro, not knowing such common sense means I'm a failure as her guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:02.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right, it's only because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Doing morning exercise by yourself?{Yo, doing a morning run by yourself?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:22.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it's just everyone else is slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what's up? You're here so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With guts, I turned in the manuscripts.{I mustered up my courage and turned in the manuscript?}{literal approach = bleh}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I sent it to the editor just now. {editor}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:37.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I would never wake up if I slept, so I went ahead and came to school. {slept}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:41.61,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36.363636}Note: Basically, she's commenting on the fact that it's rare to see Hiro come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:41.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. Maybe it'll rain tomorrow?{Has the wind changed direction? Will it rain tomorrow?}{<-more literal translation} {this is not what she said but she is trying to say something to that effect since hirono seldom goes to school}{Rain is good.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm not sure if I can stay awake in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:50.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You drank it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:55.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll praise you for the effort at least. Good job, Onii-chan. {Isn't 'Onii-chan' a proper noun?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who could it be?{cant find better sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!{You bitch.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some cute, normal prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Normal is just closing the eyes, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, normal isn't fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm getting killed for that reason!{getting killed for that reason?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:34.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you're here, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:43.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because if Hirono-kun isn't here, I can't come to this locked rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you give that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:53.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important inheritance left by my big sister after she graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about just making a spare key? {Then how about just make a spare key?}{"to make" is used, I think.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You think I would give up this valuable place to be alone just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,By the way Hirono-kun, how was work today?{By the way, Hirono-kun, how was work today?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:12.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't send in your manuscript quickly, then the editor will give you a blood bath. {check} {If you don't send in your manuscript quickly, then the editor will give you a blood bath.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:15.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If that was the situation, then I wouldn't be here at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second! Where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think? {do-ko-ka?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It looks kind of normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Normal? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's like following the book...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You see these scenes everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We made it look normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:47.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And that's because if it's not connected, your clips will leave too strong of an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:55.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A film with too much peculiarity will not be regarded as special. {A work that as a strong habit will seem obnoxious}{check please}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:59.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you're aiming to win, realistic things are better. {What? Check please}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:04.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:08.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, it's fun just to walk around Otowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living here, so I'm sick of it. {bored of it}{used to it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:16.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're walking together, don't you feel it's different than the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:23.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This Otowa place used to have normal Japanese scenery before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, most of them were destroyed after the earthquake. {Well, most of them were destroyed after the earthquake.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They got burned down during the war too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What an unlucky town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:36.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why until then, they were making a completely different town. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:44.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hold back since I did bring my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't eat much after staying up that late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What nice weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:54.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With a day like this, you won't feel like going to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:58.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you planning to skip class anyway?{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because the town is more fun than class.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:13.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I hate school; I just don't like being bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:21.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably not the one who should be saying this, but won't it be bad if you don't go to school?{I might not be the one who should say this, but wouldn't it be bad if you don't go to school?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:25.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Life wouldn't be fun if we only learned about politics and common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:30.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do whatever is fun for you too, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hiro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama?{Is this a direct statement?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:39.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Hiro-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was buying something.{I'm was?}{I went shopping...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was buying the shoujo manga, Pokkyu.{'bought'?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You really like manga, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:56.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is my younger classman, Hayama Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is my classmate, Miyamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:10.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, from now on you will call me Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?{What's up with that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:18.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot my name so easily, and now my heart is wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'm going to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:26.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayama, don't you think this is coercion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Hiro-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:32.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange that you're calling her by her last name in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:36.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Hiro-senpai sure is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?{uweeeh.....}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:46.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that if Hiro-senpai got a girlfriend then boyfriendless Kei-senpai would be mine.{I was just hoping that if Hiro-senpai got a girlfriend, then boyfriendless Kei-senpai would be mine. ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kei becoming my girlfriend now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai, looks like she dumped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, she is not my girlfriend!{Like I said}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:05.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke, I know how you feel, but please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:08.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is working hard now so we can win the next film festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you wanted to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:11.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was just worrying about the evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't everyone just do it the way we want? {Why can't everyone do it the way they want to do it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:22.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you did it that way? {So that's why the way you just did it the way you liked?}{Who what why?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been kind of boring lately.{It's been...?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I've been looking through the viewfinder. {the videocam finder}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't seem to see what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Should we break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:48.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel kind of lost... about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:56.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get me the{some kind of document} list, Miss President? {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The remains of the earthquake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:11.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:18.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to look again on what happened to these ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I always only look forward, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:26.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Isn't it the case that you can't see what you really want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:27.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:32.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,However, what I really want to do has already been decided long before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the picture that I want.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And that is of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:42.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What I really want to take... is my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:54.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The temperature wasn't all that high, but Himura-san wouldn't let me go out...{The temperature wasn't all that high, but Himura-san still didn't let me go out}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,even though I wanted to meet with Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You should listen to what Himura-san says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if it got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:23.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan, don't yawn while watching me practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude, you know.{Hey, Onii-chan, don't yawn while watching me practice. That's rude, you know?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My awake time is different than yours. {My waking time is different from yours.  Check please}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:30.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Humans sleep at night and wake up in the morning, right?{Humans sleep at night and wake up in the morning, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:34.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mangaka are really lost creatures.{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what did you want to talk about this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you skipped class yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:45.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My body was tired from staying up late after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I went back and slept in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:57.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You were with Miyamura-senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki told me. You did meet with her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know about Miyamura?{What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She's famous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:10.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who doesn't know her is you who doesn't go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:16.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because she is pretty, the boys are all over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They say skipping class is one of her habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:23.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes when she leaves from class, she doesn't listen to anything the teacher says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When asked to do an errand, she doesn't even answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:34.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan's grades are in danger, but you just follow her without knowing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:36.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublesome person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:41.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop saying bad things about someone who you barely know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:46.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So do {\i1}you{\i0} know more about Miyamura-senpai, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:52.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I only met her once during Christmas, so that's not even a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:22:03.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, so you broke our promise and went to see Miyamura-senpai instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:37.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The memories you want to deliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:39.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,should be left to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:43.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next {\i1} ef - a tale of memories:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:44.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:47.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
